From 92bc4ec1fcfc5169e305d513a9b043bb26b14b67 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ivan Melnikov <mail@melnoff.com>
Date: Fri, 24 Apr 2026 23:44:48 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] feat(ui): toggle to hide round video messages
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Adds a user-facing preference (stored via writePref/readPref) that
hides video-note messages ("кружки") from chat views. When enabled,
the Element hides itself via HiddenByUserPref flag, so it is skipped
in scroll height and rendering just like HiddenByGroup items.

Setting toggle lives in Advanced settings under a new subsection.
---
 Telegram/Resources/langs/lang.strings         |  3 ++
 Telegram/SourceFiles/core/core_settings.h     |  3 ++
 .../history/view/history_view_element.cpp     | 15 ++++++--
 .../history/view/history_view_element.h       |  1 +
 .../settings/sections/settings_advanced.cpp   | 35 +++++++++++++++++++
 5 files changed, 55 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

